SUMMARY:Animals and Ales Photo Contest Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:In collaboration with Veterinarians Without Borders North America\, we’re running a three-week-long photo contest where one lucky furry friend ends up on a limited-release brew of ours! \nFrom 2/23-3/16\, submit a photo of your pet\, and collect as many votes as possible from your family and friends ($1 = 1 vote)\, and by doing so\, raise important funds for veterinary care and programs to support animals and communities in need. The winning pet will be featured on a packaged beer label of a limited release! \nClick here to read all the official rules and requirements of each submission. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/animals-and-ales-photo-contest-fundraiser/
