SUMMARY:Free Community Event: Sing! Move! Belong!
DESCRIPTION:Come as you are. Leave more connected.\nWe’ll hold the space for you to sing\, move\, and express what’s alive in you. In community\, we remember we’re not alone. \nWe will have a table for the community to share any helpful resources. No offering is too small; you never know who will find what they need. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
